snippet.textDisplay:
The best part about the song was when both the singers were feeling the lyrics and enjoying it themselves! (:
I didn't understand the song much in the first go but truly enjoyed the music but today co incidentally it's english captions were on and Oo damnn, rabba kinni soni lyrics hai🥺🥺❤️❤️...this song still holds soo much relevance and significance EVEN TODAY!!!!🌟🥺🥺❤️❤️...one of my favs songs undoubtedly now🥺✌️🌟🥰😘😘💯💯❤️🥺🥺❤️❤️❤️❤️
And I don't know why I am kinda feeling sooo glad to hv hindi as our language which is just so unique and special to us which we don't hv to share like english!
How beautifully it potrays the deep condolences of the partition of our one piece land and the Love for our own culture and motherland targetting specifically the Youth🙏🥰❤️🥺💯👍
